1) Multiline block entering:
    Prompt should indicate indentation level:

    $ if foo:
    >     for bar in baz:
    >>         echo nonsense
    >>                      # No spaces or tabs escapes both indentation
    nonsense
    $

2) Apply separation and selection logic to strings
    $ echo "hello world!"[0]
    hello

3) Filename Expansion
    $ echo f{}
    Desktop Downloads Pictures Public 

